_sText:
Thanks to hamster for helping me start to understand how to use hammer ;)

This map was designed for use in gungame. It has the layout of a small maze, with a fountain in the middle of the map, which also has ladders above it, which allow players to access the upper level to have an advantage over the enemy. I have also included two portals in the map which allow players to quickly access the other side of the map.

I hope you like it!
